What you need to know:

The outpour of tributes in both mainstream and social media from Kenyans and the world of rugby, led by President Uhuru Kenyatta, is clear proof of Ayimba’s statusThe highlights of his stellar career was Kenya sevens team’s maiden appearance at the Olympic Games in Rio de Janeiro (2016) and their World Sevens Rugby Series victory in Singapore, also in 2016Kenya Rugby Union chairman Oduor Gangla also confirmed that “a warrior had rested”